{"uuid": "79a8fe3b-ce57-487b-b675-86fcd893ee4c", "id": 55534, "date": "2025-01-01T04:00:33", "date_gmt": "2025-01-01T12:00:33", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=55534"}, "modified": "2025-11-08T09:46:54", "modified_gmt": "2025-11-08T17:46:54", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-january-1", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/01/01/kingdom-of-days-january-1/", "title": {"rendered": "January 1"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1976:\u00a0</strong>Bruce, Steve, Roy, and David Sancious drop by The Stone Pony, where they join Southside Johnny and The Asbury Jukes on stage for several numbers.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"6338\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1976-0101/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1976-0101.jpg?fit=300%2C186&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"300,186\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1976-0101\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1976-0101.jpg?fit=300%2C186&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1976-0101.jpg?fit=300%2C186&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6338\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1976-0101-300x186.jpg?resize=758%2C470\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"470\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"15100\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/48769956123_ee290e600f_o/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/48769956123_ee290e600f_o.jpg?fit=867%2C933&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"867,933\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"48769956123_ee290e600f_o\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/48769956123_ee290e600f_o.jpg?fit=279%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/48769956123_ee290e600f_o.jpg?fit=758%2C816&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-15100\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/48769956123_ee290e600f_o-279x300.jpg?resize=758%2C815\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"815\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/48769956123_ee290e600f_o.jpg?resize=279%2C300&amp;ssl=1 279w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/48769956123_ee290e600f_o.jpg?resize=768%2C826&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/48769956123_ee290e600f_o.jpg?w=867&amp;ssl=1 867w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>The last night of the Darkness Tour in Richfield is also the longest. The 31-song setlist is highlighted by fond farewells (for a time, at least): &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/10/04/roll-of-the-dice-the-fever/\">The Fever</a>&#8221; and &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/08/04/roll-of-the-dice-meeting-across-the-river/\">Meeting Across the River</a>&#8221; won&#8217;t appear again for two decades, and &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/11/06/roll-of-the-dice-streets-of-fire/\">Streets of Fire</a>&#8221; will be absent for 24 years.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Richfield 01/01/1979\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLJTyL9twk3zDRD_Yf7sSE5kXut3NQgaUK\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>1987:\u00a0</strong>Bruce releases &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/08/05/roll-of-the-dice-fire/\">Fire</a>,&#8221; his latest single from the\u00a0<em>Live 1975-85\u00a0</em>box set collection.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen - Commercial for &quot;Fire&quot; - 1987-01-01\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/grhe4slilF8?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>2000: </strong>On the first day of the new millennium,\u00a0<em>American Top 40</em> host Casey Kasem recounts the most memorable hits and events in rock and roll history, including Bruce Springsteen&#8217;s &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/09/21/roll-of-the-dice-born-in-the-u-s-a/\">Born in the U.S.A.</a>&#8221;</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-55534-4\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/AT40-2000-01-01.mp3?_=4\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/AT40-2000-01-01.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/AT40-2000-01-01.mp3</a></audio>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Happy New Year! On this date: Bruce wraps up the Darkness Tour, releases the single for &#8220;Fire,&#8221; and plays an impromptu Stone Pony set.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 15344, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}}, "categories": [2], "tags": [508, 257, 1248, 526, 1025, 87, 26, 11], "class_list": ["post-55534", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-kingdom-of-days", "tag-darkness-tour", "tag-fire", "tag-live-1975-85", "tag-richfield", "tag-roy-bittan", "tag-southside-johnny", "tag-steve-van-zandt", "tag-stone-pony"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/19790101_front.jpg?fit=2045%2C1767&ssl=1", "jetpack_sharing_enabled": true, "jetpack_shortlink": "https://wp.me/p9w3Lk-erI", "jetpack_likes_enabled":